So then they go and test this with a complicated PK signaling pathway in HeLa cells and show that indeed if they knock out the feedback loop (using siRNA) the information transfer as measured with quantitative fluorescence decreases abruptly.

This could be interesting for me to test with the lac system by including either feedback to repress or activate the production of the repressor, or something along those lines. Let's think about it.},
